value.name: Ragdoll
value.overview: Detectives look to untangle the case of the Ragdoll Killer, who has killed six people and sewn their bodies into the shape of one grotesque body nicknamed the Ragdoll.

value.name: Ragdolly Anna
value.overview: Ragdolly Anna was a British children's television series, produced by Yorkshire Television. The show was broadcast between 1982-1987 on the ITV network during its CITV strand. The show starred Pat Coombs and was about a small stuffed doll named Ragdolly Anna that used to spring into life when nobody was watching and would go on many wild and fantastic adventures.

value.name: Untitled Bull Riding Drama Series
value.overview: A megastar rodeo champion faces crossroads in his life. He is facing a new challenge with a new up-and-coming hotshot who is absolutely fearless and threatens his well-established ways after a secret comes to light.
